---
/* Volage page header — comparison mocks.
   ------------------------------------------------------------------
   2026-05-24. Comparison surface for Stephane: the four Volage page
   header treatments (Options A / B / C / D per Pax's
   `volage-header-research.md`, Part 3) stacked vertically at full
   scale so they can be reviewed side by side before committing.

   Direct-URL only. NOT linked from the nav. The live /volage page
   stays UNTOUCHED. Same pattern as `/story-mocks` and
   `/product-mocks`.

   Source of truth: `volage-header-research.md`, Part 3.

   Information rendered in every option (identical across all four —
   what changes is the COMPOSITION, not the content):
     · Edition: First Edition
     · Name:    Volage
     · Vitola:  Canonazo
     · Tagline: A cigar that doesn't wait for an occasion.
     · Image:   `cigar-volage.png` (the existing isolated cigar-on-
                void PNG, 848 × 3334, alpha channel). Options that
                want a different image register (B's full-bleed
                scene) use a captioned placeholder built from the
                same dashed-gold-with-corners pattern used by the
                live /volage page's packaging gallery — flagged so
                the photography gap is visible at review.

   Per option, in one line:
     · A — Tagline-led (Pax's recommendation). Type column ~62% of
           grid, image column ~38%. Tagline at display Spectral
           italic is the protagonist; eyebrow combines edition +
           vitola on one row; name is signature-scale below the
           tagline. Existing PNG, no frame, soft drop shadow.
     · B — Full-bleed photographic room. Landscape placeholder runs
           edge-to-edge; type block sits bottom-left as a small
           composed caption (eyebrow + name + vitola + tagline) in
           cream over the photographic ground. Real landscape
           shoot is the dependency.
     · C — Deferred hero (two beats). Compact header keeps the
           split, with the name promoted to display scale; tagline
           pulled out as its own centred italic pull-quote in a
           second sub-section immediately below.
     · D — Typographic pause (no image in header). Pure centred
           type moment on cream: eyebrow, very-large name, vitola
           caption, gold hairline, italic tagline. Cigar image is
           deferred to section 2 of the live page. */

import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import cigarVolage from '../assets/cigar-volage.png';

// Identical content across all four options. Brief says these
// literal strings, not the JSON values (JSON has "1st Edition";
// the brief specifies "First Edition"). Hard-coded so the four
// options are unambiguously the same content.
const edition = 'First Edition';
const name    = 'Volage';
const vitola  = 'Canonazo';
const tagline = "A cigar that doesn't wait for an occasion.";
---

<BaseLayout title="Mariposa • Volage page header comparison mocks">
  <section class="intro">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="intro__eyebrow">Internal &mdash; comparison surface</p>
      <h1 class="intro__title">Volage page header &mdash; comparison mocks</h1>
      <p class="intro__lede">
        Four header treatments for the Volage product page. Same
        information in all four: First Edition, Volage, Canonazo,
        tagline. Source: Pax&rsquo;s
        <em>volage-header-research.md</em>, Part 3. The live
        <code>/volage</code> page is unchanged.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ─── Option A label ─────────────────────────────────────── */}
  <section class="label">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="label__eyebrow">
        Option A &mdash; Tagline-led
        <span class="label__pick">Pax&rsquo;s recommendation</span>
      </p>
      <p class="label__desc">
        The tagline is the protagonist at display Spectral italic
        on a 22ch measure. Edition and vitola fold into a single
        composed eyebrow row above; the name &ldquo;Volage&rdquo;
        sits beneath the tagline as a signature, not a headline.
        Existing <code>cigar-volage.png</code> on a cream ground,
        no frame, soft drop shadow. Type column ~62% of the grid,
        image column ~38%.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mock mock--a" aria-label="Option A — Tagline-led">
    <div class="mock-a__inner container">
      <div class="mock-a__copy">
        <p class="mock-a__eyebrow">
          {edition}
          <span class="mock-a__eyebrow-sep" aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
          {vitola}
        </p>
        <span class="mock-a__rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <p class="mock-a__tagline">{tagline}</p>
        <p class="mock-a__signature">{name}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mock-a__media">
        <Image
          class="mock-a__cigar"
          src={cigarVolage}
          alt={`The Mariposa ${name} cigar, ${tagline.toLowerCase()}`}
          widths={[260, 420, 640]}
          sizes="(max-width: 720px) 65vw, 30vw"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* ─── Option B label ─────────────────────────────────────── */}
  <section class="label">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="label__eyebrow">Option B &mdash; Full-bleed room</p>
      <p class="label__desc">
        Edge-to-edge landscape photograph (Davidoff Winston
        Churchill register), the cigar in its scene, type laid
        over as a small composed caption block in the bottom-left
        corner. Eyebrow + name + vitola + tagline read as
        signature on a print. A commissioned landscape shoot is
        the dependency &mdash; rendered here as a captioned
        placeholder (same dashed-gold-with-corners grammar the
        live <code>/volage</code> packaging gallery uses).
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mock mock--b" aria-label="Option B — Full-bleed room">
    <figure class="mock-b__frame placeholder" aria-label="Full-bleed landscape scene placeholder">
      <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="placeholder__corner placeholder__corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <figcaption class="placeholder__caption mock-b__placeholder-caption">
        PLACEHOLDER: commissioned landscape scene required &mdash;
        cigar in context, ambient pink / cream environment,
        generous negative space on the lower-left for the type
        overlay.
      </figcaption>
      <div class="mock-b__caption">
        <p class="mock-b__eyebrow">{edition}</p>
        <p class="mock-b__name">{name}</p>
        <p class="mock-b__vitola">{vitola}</p>
        <p class="mock-b__tagline">{tagline}</p>
      </div>
    </figure>
  </section>

  {/* ─── Option C label ─────────────────────────────────────── */}
  <section class="label">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="label__eyebrow">Option C &mdash; Deferred hero</p>
      <p class="label__desc">
        Two beats instead of one. The header keeps the split but
        compacts to ~58vh, with &ldquo;Volage&rdquo; promoted to
        display scale and a single gold hairline as the section&rsquo;s
        foot. The tagline is then extracted into its own centred
        italic pull-quote in a short sub-section immediately
        below. Same <code>cigar-volage.png</code> as Option A, no
        frame.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mock mock--c" aria-label="Option C — Deferred hero">
    <div class="mock-c__inner container">
      <div class="mock-c__media">
        <Image
          class="mock-c__cigar"
          src={cigarVolage}
          alt={`The Mariposa ${name} cigar, ${tagline.toLowerCase()}`}
          widths={[260, 420, 640]}
          sizes="(max-width: 720px) 65vw, 28vw"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="mock-c__copy">
        <p class="mock-c__eyebrow">
          {edition}
          <span class="mock-c__eyebrow-sep" aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
          {vitola}
        </p>
        <p class="mock-c__name">{name}</p>
        <span class="mock-c__rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="mock-c__pull" aria-label="Option C — pull-quote sub-section">
    <p class="mock-c__pull-text">
      <span class="mock-c__pull-quote" aria-hidden="true">&ldquo;</span>{tagline}
    </p>
  </section>

  {/* ─── Option D label ─────────────────────────────────────── */}
  <section class="label">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="label__eyebrow">Option D &mdash; Typographic pause</p>
      <p class="label__desc">
        No image in the header. Pure centred type moment on
        cream: eyebrow, very-large &ldquo;Volage&rdquo; at
        Spectral display, vitola caption, a centred gold
        hairline, italic tagline. The cigar image moves to
        section 2 (signature) on the live page. The Aesop /
        Patek 5236 register.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mock mock--d" aria-label="Option D — Typographic pause">
    <div class="mock-d__inner container">
      <p class="mock-d__eyebrow">{edition}</p>
      <p class="mock-d__name">{name}</p>
      <p class="mock-d__vitola">{vitola}</p>
      <span class="mock-d__rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <p class="mock-d__tagline">{tagline}</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ─── Intro ──────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .intro {
    padding-block: var(--space-9) var(--space-7);
    background: var(--white);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);
  }
  .intro__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-eyebrow);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-section);
    color: var(--gold-deep);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  .intro__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.4vw, 3.25rem);
    line-height: var(--lh-snug);
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }
  .intro__lede {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-lede);
    line-height: var(--lh-body);
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }
  .intro__lede code {
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
    font-size: 0.92em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  /* ─── Option labels (banner above each mock) ─────────────── */
  .label {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--white);
    padding-block: var(--space-6);
  }
  .label__eyebrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-eyebrow);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-section);
    color: var(--gold-leaf);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
  .label__pick {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-eyebrow);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-eyebrow);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--pink);
    border: 1px solid var(--pink);
    padding: 2px 8px;
  }
  .label__desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    line-height: var(--lh-body);
    color: var(--pearl);
    max-width: 72ch;
  }
  .label__desc code {
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
    font-size: 0.92em;
    color: var(--gold-soft);
  }

  /* ─── Shared mock chrome ─────────────────────────────────── */
  .mock {
    background: var(--white);
  }

  /* ─── Option A — Tagline-led ─────────────────────────────── */
  /* 88–95vh. Pearl ground. 62 / 38 split with the tagline as
     protagonist on the wider column. No frame; soft directional
     drop shadow on the PNG. */
  .mock--a {
    background: var(--pearl);
    min-height: 88vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding-block: clamp(var(--space-8), 10vw, var(--space-10));
  }
  .mock-a__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 62fr 38fr;
    gap: clamp(var(--space-7), 7vw, var(--space-10));
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .mock-a__copy {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .mock-a__eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-eyebrow);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-eyebrow);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold-deep);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-5) 0;
  }
  .mock-a__eyebrow-sep {
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }
  .mock-a__rule {
    display: block;
    width: 120px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold-leaf);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  .mock-a__tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4.2rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 22ch;
  }
  .mock-a__signature {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.6vw, 1.3rem);
    line-height: var(--lh-snug);
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: var(--space-6) 0 0 0;
  }
  .mock-a__media {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
  }
  .mock-a__cigar {
    width: auto;
    max-width: 70%;
    max-height: 70vh;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 24px 40px rgba(31, 27, 23, 0.18));
  }

  /* ─── Option B — Full-bleed room ─────────────────────────── */
  /* 92vh, edge-to-edge landscape scene. Type overlay block sits in
     the bottom-left corner. Real shoot is the dependency; the
     placeholder retains the same dashed-gold-with-corners grammar
     used on the live /volage packaging gallery. */
  .mock--b {
    /* Break out of the container to true viewport width. */
    width: 100vw;
    margin-inline: calc(50% - 50vw);
    padding: 0;
  }
  .mock-b__frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 92vh;
    margin: 0;
    /* Reuse the placeholder grammar — pearl ground, dashed gold
       border, four corner ticks. The placeholder caption sits at
       centre; the type overlay sits at bottom-left. */
    background: var(--pearl);
    border: 1px dashed var(--gold-deep);
    display: block;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .mock-b__placeholder-caption {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    max-width: 36ch;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    line-height: var(--lh-snug);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    color: var(--gold-deep);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .mock-b__caption {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: clamp(var(--space-6), 5vw, var(--space-8));
    left: clamp(var(--space-6), 5vw, var(--space-8));
    max-width: 42ch;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }
  .mock-b__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-eyebrow);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-eyebrow);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold-deep);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .mock-b__name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 4.8vw, 3.6rem);
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-display);
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .mock-b__vitola {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-eyebrow);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-eyebrow);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold-deep);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .mock-b__tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.6vw, 1.35rem);
    line-height: var(--lh-snug);
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: var(--space-3) 0 0 0;
    max-width: 38ch;
  }

  /* ─── Option C — Deferred hero (two beats) ───────────────── */
  .mock--c {
    background: var(--white);
    min-height: 58vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding-block: clamp(var(--space-7), 7vw, var(--space-9));
  }
  .mock-c__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 38fr 52fr;
    gap: clamp(var(--space-7), 7vw, var(--space-10));
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .mock-c__media {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
  }
  .mock-c__cigar {
    width: auto;
    max-width: 80%;
    max-height: 52vh;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 18px 36px rgba(31, 27, 23, 0.16));
  }
  .mock-c__copy {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .mock-c__eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-eyebrow);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-eyebrow);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold-deep);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-5) 0;
  }
  .mock-c__eyebrow-sep {
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }
  .mock-c__name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(3.6rem, 7vw, 5.4rem);
    line-height: 0.92;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-display);
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .mock-c__rule {
    display: block;
    width: 140px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold-leaf);
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
  }
  /* Pull-quote sub-section — 18vh cream/pearl band. */
  .mock-c__pull {
    background: var(--pearl);
    min-height: 18vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-block: var(--space-7);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
  }
  .mock-c__pull-text {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
    line-height: var(--lh-snug);
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 30ch;
    text-align: center;
    text-indent: -0.3em;
  }
  .mock-c__pull-quote {
    color: var(--gold-deep);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ─── Option D — Typographic pause ───────────────────────── */
  .mock--d {
    background: var(--pearl);
    min-height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-block: clamp(var(--space-8), 10vw, var(--space-10));
  }
  .mock-d__inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  .mock-d__eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-eyebrow);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-eyebrow);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold-deep);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-5) 0;
  }
  .mock-d__name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(4.4rem, 9vw, 7rem);
    line-height: 0.96;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-display);
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .mock-d__vitola {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-eyebrow);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-eyebrow);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold-deep);
    margin: var(--space-4) 0 0 0;
  }
  .mock-d__rule {
    display: block;
    width: 80px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold-leaf);
    margin: var(--space-6) 0;
  }
  .mock-d__tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    line-height: var(--lh-snug);
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 28ch;
  }

  /* ─── Placeholder grammar (reused from /volage) ──────────── */
  .placeholder__corner {
    position: absolute;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-deep);
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .placeholder__corner--tl { top: -1px;    left: -1px;  border-right: 0; border-bottom: 0; }
  .placeholder__corner--tr { top: -1px;    right: -1px; border-left: 0;  border-bottom: 0; }
  .placeholder__corner--bl { bottom: -1px; left: -1px;  border-right: 0; border-top: 0; }
  .placeholder__corner--br { bottom: -1px; right: -1px; border-left: 0;  border-top: 0; }

  /* ─── Mobile ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .mock-a__inner,
    .mock-c__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-7);
    }
    .mock-a__copy,
    .mock-c__copy {
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .mock-a__rule,
    .mock-c__rule {
      margin-inline: auto;
    }
    .mock-a__cigar,
    .mock-c__cigar {
      max-width: 65vw;
    }
    .mock-b__frame {
      height: 80vh;
    }
    .mock-b__caption {
      bottom: var(--space-5);
      left: var(--space-5);
      right: var(--space-5);
      max-width: none;
    }
  }
</style>
